<br>
As long as there are non RP players who insist playing on the only RP server in EQ because they think it is their God Given Right, we will never have an RP server.   It just gets worse with time instead of better.<br>
<br>
I am sorely disappointed in Verant for not make a completely RP server as well.  There will always be people/groups/guilds, etc who want to ruin the RP fun for their own personal gains.  It is unfortunate Verant allows it and there is little we as players can do about it.<br>
<br>
I see FV server as nothing more than a deity/race server, not an RP server.  I am very sorry to admit that.  It is not at all what I was hoping it would be and is because of those who have no respect for us who just want to roleplay and be happy.<br>
<br>
I really expected this server to be different in attitude but it is not.  It is what the game itself makes kind hearted people become, greedy and assholistic.  So, this server will not ever be a RP server as long as Verant does nothing to support us roleplayers.  It was a cruel joke that VI did to us.  For me it was the last straw of hope for the game.<br>
